title: Check your Online Privacy
extract: Internet privacy is the privacy and security level of personal data published via the Internet. It is a broad term that refers to a variety of factors, techniques and technologies used to protect sensitive and private data, communications, and preferences. ... Internet privacy is also known as online privacy.
